						<summary>

						<p>Same wall.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Vīrarājēndradēva: Date lost: c. 13th century.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription is damaged and incomplete and the date portion is lost. It seems to record some gift made by a certain Vīrarājēndra-Aṇittirap-pallavaraiyaṉ, to the image of Dakshiṇāmūrtti set up by some <hi rend="italic">maṉṟāḍis</hi> and priests.</p>						

